An interactive Excel Sales Analysis Dashboard that transforms raw sales data into actionable business
insights. This project analyzes sales performance from 2020–2022 using Pivot Tables, Pivot Charts, Slicers, KPIs, and dynamic visualizations to track revenue trends
, product performance, customer behavior, and regional sales. Designed to support data-driven decision-making through clear and interactive reporting.

📊 Features
- Interactive Dashboard
- Sales Performance Analysis (2020–2022)
- KPI Tracking
- Revenue Trend Analysis
- Product Performance Analysis
- Customer Insights
- Regional Sales Analysis
- Dynamic Filtering with Slicers
- Business Insights & Decision Support

🛠️ Tools Used
- Microsoft Excel
- Pivot Tables
- Pivot Charts
- Slicers
- Data Cleaning
- Conditional Formatting
- Business Intelligence
